subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Maria Sharapova’s 7-5, 6-3 victory over Ana Ivanovic at the Australian Open earned her a third Grand Slam singles title to go with those she won at Wimbledon in 2004 and the U.S. Open in 2006.
